<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your Tickets Are Ready!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f5f5f5; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        .ticket-box { background: #f8f9fa; border: 2px dashed #dee2e6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .qr-code { text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background: #667eea; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; }
        .important { background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üé´ Your Tickets Are Ready!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi {{user.name}},</p>
            <p>Great news! Your tickets have been successfully purchased and are ready for use.</p>
            
            <div class="ticket-box">
                <h2>üìç Event Details</h2>
                <p><strong>Event:</strong> {{event.name}}</p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{event.date}}</p>
                <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{event.time}}</p>
                <p><strong>Venue:</strong> {{event.venue}}</p>
                <p><strong>Tickets:</strong> {{ticketCount}} √ó {{ticketType}}</p>
                <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> #{{orderId}}</p>
            </div>
            
            {{#if nftMinted}}
            <div class="important">
                <strong>üéâ NFT Tickets Minted!</strong><br>
                Your tickets have been minted as NFTs and are available in your wallet.
                Transaction ID: {{transactionId}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{ticketUrl}}" class="button">View Your Tickets</a>
            </div>
            
            <h3>What's Next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Save this email for your records</li>
                <li>Add the event to your calendar</li>
                <li>Download the TicketToken mobile app for easy entry</li>
                {{#if transferable}}
                <li>You can transfer or sell these tickets on our marketplace</li>
                {{/if}}
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, contact us at {{supportEmail}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2024 TicketToken. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="{{privacyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
